
Code for Seeeduino-based tricopter.


need to install pyserial and pygame modules.

seeeduino should keep a logfile.


Calculations are done at 40 Hz.
Watchdog is fed at 10 Hz.
Controls are sent at 20 Hz?


Looks like I'm going to use pidquadcontroller code for IMU: code.google.com/p/picquadcontroller/source/browse/trunk/imu.h?r=7

And AeroQuad code for PID.



The control system works something like this:

################################################################################
#                                                                              #
# **************************                                                   #
# * BMA180                 * --------.                                         #
# * (3-axis accelerometer) *         |                                         #
# **************************         |                                         #
#                                    |                                         #
# *****************               ***********************************          #
# * ITG-3200      * ------------- * IMU (inertial measurement unit) *          #
# * (3-axis gyro) *               ***********************************          #
# *****************                              |                             #
#                                                |                             #
#                                      *************************************** #
#                                      *                                     * #
# *************************            *                                     * #
# * Other peripherals     *            *                                     * #
# * (not yet implemented) *            *                                     * #
# *   - Sensors           * ---------- *          MAIN SOFTWARE LOOP         * #
# *   - Camera            *            *                                     * #
# *   - GPS               *            *                  ON                 * #
# *   - Lights            *            *                                     * #
# *************************            *           SSEEEDUINO MEGA           * #
#                             .------- *                                     * #
#                             |        *                                     * #
# ************                | .----- *                                     * #
# * Watchdog * ---------------' |      *                                     * #
# ************                  |      *************************************** #
#                               |                                              #
# *********                     |                                              #
# * Pilot * --------------------'                                              #
# *********                                                                    #
#       |                                                                      #
#       |                                                                      #
#       |                                                                      #
#       '------------------------------.                                       #
#                                      |                                       #
#                                      |                                       #
#                                      |                                       #
#                                 ************                                 #
#                                 * DOWNLINK *                                 #
#                                 ************                                 #
#                                                                              #
################################################################################

